    "Name": "Thunderbolt",
    "Details": "Used by the lance commander of Lamenkov's Liability, this Thunderbolt removes the Snub-Nose PPC of the original TDR-10M and replaces it with a C3 master computer and an additional Light PPC in the left torso. In every other respect, it is a standard TDR-10M.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Multi Trac</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>",
